The '''Rhysode Room''' was a meeting room in the [[Jedi Academy (Ossus)|Jedi Academy]] on [[Ossus/Legends|Ossus]]. It was named after the deceased [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Ganner Rhysode]] who [[Battle of the World-Well|died in combat]] against the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. A large room centered by an expensive [[roo-wood]] serenity table flanked by [[flowfit chair]]s, the room was greatly contrasted by the sparse decor of the academy. It was here that [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] intended to present the delegates from [[Ithor/Legends|Ithor]] possible new home planet she and [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] discovered. [[Ooamu Waoabi]], the eldest of the [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorians]], would have accepted her offer except for sudden arrival of [[Chief of State (Galactic Alliance)|Chief of State]] [[Cal Omas]]. To prevent possible [[The Colony|Killik]]-[[Chiss Ascendancy/Legends|Chiss]] war, Organa Solo mentioned their discovery. Omas with all presented [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] then agreed to give newly found world to [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] as replacement for planet [[Qoribu]] that was source of previous [[Skirmish at Qoribu|dispute]].

